Geislingen: More than 100 young Catholics from the little ones Heuberg reaffirm their faith in the occasion
In two worship services are 101 15- and 16-year-old young people of the ministry unit On Small Heuberg gefirmt been.
Accompanied the service in the morning the group Laudato-Si, on the afternoon of the youth choir The Spirit.
With the reception of the firm Sakraments said yes to the young people of their baptism and enlisted the power of the Holy Spirit.
The firm has had in the past few months, under the direction of Reiner Dehner deacon and with the help of a number of community members prepared for the big day.
In various projects learned they know different tasks of the Christian community in this life and experienced the Untermachtal Youth Day together.
